I bought this because I am a big Roxanne Brewer fan, and it does not disappoint!  There are some hardcore scenes, which is a little unusual for a Something Weird title, so be forewarned there.  But Roxy makes plenty of topless and nude appearances and that's what I was looking for!

What a great movie for Uschi Digard. if you like her movies, then you should add this one to your collection. the movie has everything gathered in a funny story, also it has about 90% of the time nudity for females, and males front, back, side, close up, focus you name it, and off course the few minutes here and there of sexploitation, (BJ), and full intercourse right in front of your eye not only once but several times, and the women are all pretty. This movie is worth what you pay for it, and you will watch it many times and laugh every time , and you will add it to your great sexploitation movie collection.
